<title>UK: UBS sets call warrants on itself.</title>
<headline>UBS sets call warrants on itself.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Union Bank of Switzerland said it has issued 20 million American-style call warrants on bearer shares of itself.</p>
<p>One share is contolled by 50 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    1,600 CHF		 PREMIUM	14.4 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     2.22 CHF		  GEARING	13.5 TIMES</p>
<p> EXERCISE PERIOD 30.MAY.97-17.JUL.98   PAYDATE	30.MAY.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   SWISS		     MIN EXER LOT 100</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
</text>
